1
00:01:28,158 --> 00:01:33,386
[Adapted from Che Ye Liu Xiang's
novel of the same name]

2
00:01:33,386 --> 00:01:38,088
[Episode 6]

3
00:02:37,541 --> 00:02:39,114
You're back, Big Bro.

4
00:02:44,233 --> 00:02:45,400
That's a lot of stuff.

5
00:02:45,400 --> 00:02:47,441
You should've called me to help you carry it.

6
00:02:47,441 --> 00:02:48,952
It's not that much.

7
00:02:56,733 --> 00:02:57,734
Big Bro.

8
00:02:57,734 --> 00:03:00,256
You left your phone in the bag.

9
00:03:01,400 --> 00:03:03,233
The screen is cracked.

10
00:03:03,233 --> 00:03:04,400
Just throw it in the trash.

11
00:03:04,400 --> 00:03:08,400
But other than the screen,
everything else works fine.

12
00:03:08,400 --> 00:03:10,900
It's too much trouble to fix.

13
00:03:10,900 --> 00:03:14,358
It's a waste to throw it away
if it can be fixed.

14
00:03:14,358 --> 00:03:16,358
You can have it if you want it.

15
00:03:16,358 --> 00:03:17,816
Take it and fix it yourself.

16
00:03:17,816 --> 00:03:19,566
Give it to me?

17
00:03:19,566 --> 00:03:21,066
It's broken anyway.

18
00:03:21,066 --> 00:03:22,800
If you don't want it, throw it away.

19
00:03:22,800 --> 00:03:24,488
I want it.

20
00:03:46,691 --> 00:03:48,150
Big Bro.

21
00:03:48,150 --> 00:03:50,358
You have a pimple on your face today.

22
00:03:50,358 --> 00:03:52,951
Eat less of the tiger-skin peppers today.

23
00:03:54,775 --> 00:03:56,047
A pimple?

24
00:03:57,233 --> 00:03:59,441
Where?

25
00:03:59,441 --> 00:04:01,396
Right here.

26
00:04:05,400 --> 00:04:07,025
Where?

27
00:04:07,025 --> 00:04:08,534
Here.

28
00:04:25,066 --> 00:04:26,525
Eat.

29
00:04:27,941 --> 00:04:29,161
Eat.

30
00:04:30,275 --> 00:04:33,566
Eat... what?

31
00:04:33,566 --> 00:04:35,465
Let's eat.

32
00:05:07,566 --> 00:05:09,464
Stay over tonight.

33
00:05:20,566 --> 00:05:23,125
Wait, let me do the dishes first.

34
00:05:24,983 --> 00:05:27,325
I'll do the dishes first.

35
00:05:30,858 --> 00:05:33,444
I'll take a shower first.

36
00:05:39,983 --> 00:05:43,507
You can wait, but can it?

37
00:06:07,566 --> 00:06:09,950
I bought you so many briefs.

38
00:06:11,566 --> 00:06:13,996
Why are you still wearing boxers?

39
00:06:15,482 --> 00:06:16,566
They...

40
00:06:16,566 --> 00:06:19,150
They're uncomfortable.

41
00:06:19,150 --> 00:06:20,966
How about this?

42
00:06:31,275 --> 00:06:33,501
Is this comfortable?

43
00:06:59,233 --> 00:07:01,466
I'd better take a shower first.

44
00:07:43,900 --> 00:07:45,507
Fan Fan.

45
00:07:51,191 --> 00:07:53,108
I've already spoken to Lv Xin.

46
00:07:53,108 --> 00:07:55,200
Don't worry.

47
00:09:13,233 --> 00:09:15,548
Big Bro, I'm going back now.

48
00:09:17,400 --> 00:09:19,408
Stay here.

49
00:09:36,483 --> 00:09:39,024
Let's go. I'll take you
to get your phone fixed.

50
00:09:51,733 --> 00:09:54,493
Big Bro. Here's the key.

51
00:09:55,858 --> 00:09:57,956
Just keep what I give you.

52
00:10:06,441 --> 00:10:07,989
Looks wonderful.

53
00:10:09,150 --> 00:10:10,616
The scarf?

54
00:10:12,400 --> 00:10:15,899
The scarf is quite warm, too.

55
00:10:20,608 --> 00:10:21,733
Let's go.

56
00:10:21,733 --> 00:10:23,054
Okay.

57
00:10:29,566 --> 00:10:31,566
Hello. How can I help you?

58
00:10:31,566 --> 00:10:32,650
I'm going to the ministry first.

59
00:10:32,650 --> 00:10:33,691
Call me if anything comes up.

60
00:10:33,691 --> 00:10:35,002
Okay.

61
00:10:37,150 --> 00:10:39,191
Sir, I have a phone here.

62
00:10:39,191 --> 00:10:40,999
Can you see if it can be fixed?

63
00:10:43,108 --> 00:10:44,858
It can't be repaired.
The whole component needs to be replaced.

64
00:10:44,858 --> 00:10:47,441
I'll need to order the part,
and it might take a few days.

65
00:10:47,441 --> 00:10:48,441
That's fine.

66
00:10:48,441 --> 00:10:50,400
I'll just come pick it up in a few days.

67
00:10:50,400 --> 00:10:52,960
Okay. Leave a 50-yuan deposit first.

68
00:10:53,900 --> 00:10:54,900
Here you go, sir.

69
00:10:54,900 --> 00:10:56,441
Keep it safe.

70
00:10:56,441 --> 00:10:57,938
Thank you.

71
00:10:59,475 --> 00:11:01,941
[Coffee]

72
00:11:01,941 --> 00:11:03,442
Big Bro.

73
00:11:07,441 --> 00:11:10,282
You still remember that I like these beans.

74
00:11:20,066 --> 00:11:21,691
What are you doing?

75
00:11:21,691 --> 00:11:23,150
Don't need it?

76
00:11:23,150 --> 00:11:25,411
- Forget it then.
- Hey.

77
00:11:26,775 --> 00:11:28,691
Once you write this check,

78
00:11:28,691 --> 00:11:31,466
I won't see you for a long time again.

79
00:11:36,150 --> 00:11:38,441
Every day, you're either sleeping at home

80
00:11:38,441 --> 00:11:42,025
or hanging out with your friends.

81
00:11:42,025 --> 00:11:43,858
As your brother,

82
00:11:43,858 --> 00:11:47,400
I really don't know how to get along with you.

83
00:11:47,400 --> 00:11:50,691
Why don't you use this check
to start a small business?

84
00:11:50,691 --> 00:11:54,041
Take the chance to see
how the world has changed.

85
00:11:55,941 --> 00:11:58,858
I'm not talking about having fun.

86
00:11:58,858 --> 00:12:02,358
I'm talking about how
the world's operating logic has changed.

87
00:12:02,358 --> 00:12:04,066
Once you broaden your horizons,

88
00:12:04,066 --> 00:12:06,400
we'll naturally have more to talk about.

89
00:12:06,400 --> 00:12:08,200
Don't you think so?

90
00:12:09,900 --> 00:12:12,075
There's one more condition.

91
00:12:12,900 --> 00:12:15,275
The Lu family is coming
to Yunjing in a few days.

92
00:12:15,275 --> 00:12:18,445
As their daughter-in-law,
you have to treat them well.

93
00:12:21,066 --> 00:12:22,400
Ow, ow! Big Bro!

94
00:12:22,400 --> 00:12:24,060
I promise!

95
00:12:31,150 --> 00:12:32,983
So, what are we eating later?

96
00:12:32,983 --> 00:12:35,608
I know a Japanese restaurant
nearby that's really good.

97
00:12:35,608 --> 00:12:38,275
Are you going to see Lu Xiao Fan again?

98
00:12:38,275 --> 00:12:41,275
You're more attentive to
your fake brother-in-law than your own sister.

99
00:12:41,275 --> 00:12:42,983
Just remember to keep your promise.

100
00:12:42,983 --> 00:12:44,783
Hey.

101
00:12:58,441 --> 00:12:59,983
<i>Mom.</i>

102
00:12:59,983 --> 00:13:02,275
<i>Wei Wei and I are in a fake marriage.</i>

103
00:13:02,275 --> 00:13:04,816
<i>Sam is my friend.</i>

104
00:13:04,816 --> 00:13:06,900
<i>Friend?</i>

105
00:13:06,900 --> 00:13:08,108
<i>Friend.</i>

106
00:13:08,108 --> 00:13:09,608
<i>Lover.</i>

107
00:13:09,608 --> 00:13:10,733
<i>Mom.</i>

108
00:13:10,733 --> 00:13:13,400
<i>It's not easy for gay people
to find someone they're compatible with.</i>

109
00:13:13,400 --> 00:13:16,275
<i>It's very hard to just
make do and live together.</i>

110
00:13:16,275 --> 00:13:18,441
<i>That's why Sam and I cherish each other.</i>

111
00:13:18,441 --> 00:13:19,733
Is it really that touching?

112
00:13:19,733 --> 00:13:22,691
<i>Look. Among our friends,
these so-called "normal couples"...</i>

113
00:13:22,691 --> 00:13:25,791
They're all actually quite pitiful.

114
00:13:28,941 --> 00:13:31,400
Especially that white guy.

115
00:13:31,400 --> 00:13:34,858
He never belonged in their world.

116
00:13:34,858 --> 00:13:37,150
What happened between Wei Tong and Wei Wei...

117
00:13:37,150 --> 00:13:41,034
It must be very heartbreaking to him.

118
00:13:43,775 --> 00:13:45,445
Really?

119
00:13:47,400 --> 00:13:49,691
Don't you think so?

120
00:13:49,691 --> 00:13:53,454
Simon was actually betrayed by Wei Tong.

121
00:13:54,775 --> 00:13:58,150
From now on, he'll only be

122
00:13:58,150 --> 00:14:00,175
the most marginalized person in this family.

123
00:14:09,066 --> 00:14:10,546
Fan Fan.

124
00:14:11,858 --> 00:14:14,467
You don't need to overthink things.

125
00:14:23,066 --> 00:14:24,150
Are you hungry?

126
00:14:24,150 --> 00:14:26,497
I'll take you out to eat.

127
00:14:29,691 --> 00:14:31,947
Let's eat something else then.

128
00:14:50,900 --> 00:14:53,885
My parents are coming tomorrow.

129
00:15:15,233 --> 00:15:17,378
I went and bought some things.

130
00:15:18,233 --> 00:15:21,233
These two sets are for your father.

131
00:15:21,233 --> 00:15:23,900
These two are for your mother.

132
00:15:23,900 --> 00:15:26,025
This nightgown is for her, too.

133
00:15:26,025 --> 00:15:28,650
The fabric is very comfortable.

134
00:15:28,650 --> 00:15:30,566
This jacket is for your younger sister.

135
00:15:30,566 --> 00:15:33,400
Young people should dress more fashionably.

136
00:15:33,400 --> 00:15:35,515
This bracelet is for her, too.

137
00:15:38,233 --> 00:15:39,358
Big Bro.

138
00:15:39,358 --> 00:15:40,650
My sister is still young.

139
00:15:40,650 --> 00:15:43,400
She doesn't need such an expensive bracelet.

140
00:15:43,400 --> 00:15:46,452
This is what young people like these days.

141
00:15:47,816 --> 00:15:49,566
I have things to do, so I'll head out.

142
00:15:49,566 --> 00:15:52,650
When they arrive,
I might not have time to host them.

143
00:15:52,650 --> 00:15:54,412
Don't feel burdened by it.

144
00:15:55,441 --> 00:15:57,487
Okay. Thank you.

145
00:16:27,108 --> 00:16:28,150
Big Bro.

146
00:16:28,150 --> 00:16:31,150
You forgot your scarf.

147
00:16:31,150 --> 00:16:33,566
<i>That's not mine.</i>

148
00:16:33,566 --> 00:16:37,994
I saw you with a similar one last time.

149
00:16:40,191 --> 00:16:42,431
<i>Oh, you...</i>

150
00:17:09,691 --> 00:17:11,858
Hello? Big Bro?

151
00:17:11,858 --> 00:17:13,658
<i>What's wrong?</i>

152
00:17:14,400 --> 00:17:16,233
I'm still a bit worried.

153
00:17:16,233 --> 00:17:18,191
Lv Xin didn't want to come this morning.

154
00:17:18,191 --> 00:17:19,483
I'm afraid...

155
00:17:19,483 --> 00:17:20,608
<i>Fan Fan.</i>

156
00:17:20,608 --> 00:17:21,650
<i>It's too noisy over there.</i>

157
00:17:21,650 --> 00:17:23,191
- Can you hear me?
<i>- I really can't hear you.</i>

158
00:17:23,191 --> 00:17:25,400
Hello? Big Bro?

159
00:17:25,400 --> 00:17:27,066
<i>You just have to pick them up safely.</i>

160
00:17:27,066 --> 00:17:28,565
<i>Everything is arranged.</i>

161
00:17:31,150 --> 00:17:32,946
All right.

162
00:17:45,150 --> 00:17:47,650
Dad, why did you bring so many things?

163
00:17:47,650 --> 00:17:49,441
Ask your mother.

164
00:17:49,441 --> 00:17:52,483
How could we come empty-handed
on our first visit?

165
00:17:52,483 --> 00:17:55,275
Things you can buy in a store
aren't anything special.

166
00:17:55,275 --> 00:17:57,191
The Bei family is rich,
they can buy anything.

167
00:17:57,191 --> 00:18:00,441
If we're bringing gifts,
we should bring things money can't buy.

168
00:18:00,441 --> 00:18:02,858
Mom, why are your eyes so red?

169
00:18:02,858 --> 00:18:05,275
She found out she was taking the train.

170
00:18:05,275 --> 00:18:08,025
She was so excited,
she couldn't sleep all night.

171
00:18:08,025 --> 00:18:10,150
So annoying. It's because of the train.

172
00:18:10,150 --> 00:18:11,900
It was rocking and swaying.

173
00:18:11,900 --> 00:18:13,816
And with so many people sleeping together,

174
00:18:13,816 --> 00:18:15,400
how could we sleep well?

175
00:18:15,400 --> 00:18:16,566
I like taking the sleeper train.

176
00:18:16,566 --> 00:18:18,400
It feels like sleeping in a cradle.

177
00:18:18,400 --> 00:18:20,816
Rocking and swaying...
I fall asleep in no time.

178
00:18:20,816 --> 00:18:21,816
You silly girl.

179
00:18:21,816 --> 00:18:23,383
You're too old to be in a cradle.

180
00:18:23,383 --> 00:18:25,350
Look at how happy you are.

181
00:18:43,066 --> 00:18:44,983
Why aren't we staying at your home?

182
00:18:44,983 --> 00:18:46,900
It's too crowded at home.

183
00:18:46,900 --> 00:18:49,358
I was afraid you wouldn't sleep well.

184
00:18:49,358 --> 00:18:50,441
This is a grand hotel.

185
00:18:50,441 --> 00:18:52,122
Lv Xin specially arranged it.

186
00:18:53,191 --> 00:18:54,691
It's not easy for you to visit Yunjing.

187
00:18:54,691 --> 00:18:55,816
You need to rest well at night,

188
00:18:55,816 --> 00:18:58,281
so you'll have energy to sightsee by day.

189
00:18:59,775 --> 00:19:00,817
Silly child.

190
00:19:00,817 --> 00:19:02,941
Your dad and I are used to hard beds.

191
00:19:02,941 --> 00:19:05,233
We could've just slept on the floor.

192
00:19:05,233 --> 00:19:08,233
Besides, spending your money
is like spending ours.

193
00:19:08,233 --> 00:19:11,025
It's not worth wasting it on a place like this.

194
00:19:11,025 --> 00:19:12,067
Old Wu.

195
00:19:12,067 --> 00:19:14,897
Let's go to the Bei house to see Lv Xin first.

196
00:19:16,733 --> 00:19:18,396
Let's go, Old Wu.

197
00:19:26,400 --> 00:19:28,608
Fan Fan, you look so handsome.

198
00:19:28,608 --> 00:19:30,441
Auntie Lin, my parents are here.

199
00:19:30,441 --> 00:19:31,483
Fan Fan's mom.

200
00:19:31,483 --> 00:19:33,150
Fan Fan is here.

201
00:19:33,150 --> 00:19:35,150
Mom. Look at their yard.

202
00:19:35,150 --> 00:19:36,275
It's just like the pond at our house.

203
00:19:36,275 --> 00:19:38,400
- It's full of weeds.
- Hush, child! Don't talk nonsense.

204
00:19:38,400 --> 00:19:40,941
The whole family has no manners.

205
00:19:40,941 --> 00:19:42,566
It's so nice.

206
00:19:42,566 --> 00:19:44,983
Who's that running around?

207
00:19:44,983 --> 00:19:47,346
Auntie Lin just tidied up.

208
00:19:48,608 --> 00:19:50,892
The house was just cleaned.

209
00:19:52,150 --> 00:19:55,025
Don't you have any manners?

210
00:19:55,025 --> 00:19:56,066
Get down here, you girl!

211
00:19:56,066 --> 00:19:57,400
How can you run around in someone's house?

212
00:19:57,400 --> 00:19:58,608
What do you mean "someone's house"?

213
00:19:58,608 --> 00:20:00,405
This is my brother's house.

214
00:20:02,275 --> 00:20:03,566
The child is just curious.

215
00:20:03,566 --> 00:20:04,816
Let her have a look.

216
00:20:04,816 --> 00:20:06,525
Lv Xin, you're a grown-up.

217
00:20:06,525 --> 00:20:09,233
Don't mind your sister-in-law's curiosity.

218
00:20:09,233 --> 00:20:10,691
Lv Xin.

219
00:20:10,691 --> 00:20:12,493
My parents are here.

220
00:20:14,066 --> 00:20:15,977
Dad, Mom.

221
00:20:17,233 --> 00:20:18,275
Darling.

222
00:20:18,275 --> 00:20:20,851
Has your health improved over the years?

223
00:20:24,233 --> 00:20:26,233
I'm fine.

224
00:20:26,233 --> 00:20:27,275
Xiao Fan.

225
00:20:27,275 --> 00:20:29,400
Did you take Mom and Dad to the hotel?

226
00:20:29,400 --> 00:20:31,400
I specially booked that hotel.

227
00:20:31,400 --> 00:20:34,066
It's closer to the tourist attractions.

228
00:20:34,066 --> 00:20:35,275
We're not staying in a hotel.

229
00:20:35,275 --> 00:20:37,608
We'll just sleep on the floor here.

230
00:20:37,608 --> 00:20:38,775
Let's not waste that money.

231
00:20:38,775 --> 00:20:40,842
But how will we all fit?

232
00:20:43,025 --> 00:20:44,150
How about this?

233
00:20:44,150 --> 00:20:46,025
I'll call your brother.

234
00:20:46,025 --> 00:20:48,275
Let my parents stay in his room.

235
00:20:48,275 --> 00:20:51,075
- What do you think?
- No.

236
00:20:52,358 --> 00:20:55,906
Big Bro, why aren't
your things in Lv Xin's room?

237
00:20:57,816 --> 00:21:00,531
Fan Fan, where do you sleep at night?

238
00:21:01,858 --> 00:21:02,983
I stay in the attic.

239
00:21:02,983 --> 00:21:04,691
I have a lot of work at night,

240
00:21:04,691 --> 00:21:06,413
and I don't want to disturb Lv Xin.

241
00:21:10,566 --> 00:21:13,441
What kind of married couple
sleeps in separate rooms?

242
00:21:13,441 --> 00:21:15,066
This is nonsense.

243
00:21:15,066 --> 00:21:17,150
Your mom and I were saying at home,

244
00:21:17,150 --> 00:21:20,441
it's been five years,
and you still don't have a child.

245
00:21:20,441 --> 00:21:21,691
That's enough.

246
00:21:21,691 --> 00:21:22,900
They're adults now.

247
00:21:22,900 --> 00:21:25,233
They can think for themselves.

248
00:21:25,233 --> 00:21:27,691
Besides, work is important, too.

249
00:21:27,691 --> 00:21:30,191
Then, we'll stay in Fan Fan's room.

250
00:21:30,191 --> 00:21:32,233
Fan Fan, you move back to Lv Xin's room.

251
00:21:32,233 --> 00:21:33,941
Don't work for the next few days,

252
00:21:33,941 --> 00:21:36,357
so you don't disturb your wife's rest.

253
00:21:38,025 --> 00:21:39,067
I almost forgot.

254
00:21:39,067 --> 00:21:40,233
Lunch is almost ready.

255
00:21:40,233 --> 00:21:41,316
Let's all go to the living room.

256
00:21:41,316 --> 00:21:44,028
You've come so far and haven't had tea.

257
00:21:49,191 --> 00:21:51,200
Mom, let's go.

258
00:22:00,941 --> 00:22:01,983
I'm at my limit.

259
00:22:01,983 --> 00:22:03,400
I really can't eat another bite.

260
00:22:03,400 --> 00:22:04,691
I told you to eat less.

261
00:22:04,691 --> 00:22:05,691
Now that I've brought you here,

262
00:22:05,691 --> 00:22:08,025
I won't let you suffer when it comes to food.

263
00:22:09,400 --> 00:22:11,858
As expected of a servant
in a wealthy household,

264
00:22:11,858 --> 00:22:14,025
her cooking skills are top-notch.

265
00:22:14,025 --> 00:22:15,358
Auntie Lin is our helper.

266
00:22:15,358 --> 00:22:16,900
She's been with us since I was a child.

267
00:22:16,900 --> 00:22:18,466
She's not a "servant."

268
00:22:23,025 --> 00:22:25,811
Look at my big mouth. That's what I meant.

269
00:22:28,191 --> 00:22:30,400
Mom, Dad, if you're done eating,
go upstairs and rest.

270
00:22:30,400 --> 00:22:31,441
I'm leaving now.

271
00:22:31,441 --> 00:22:32,900
The elders haven't even moved yet,

272
00:22:32,900 --> 00:22:35,150
but the junior is already taking off.

273
00:22:35,150 --> 00:22:37,191
The Bei family has a habit of taking naps.

274
00:22:37,191 --> 00:22:41,066
Dad, Mom, you can rest in my room in a bit.

275
00:22:41,066 --> 00:22:43,065
I have some things to do outside.

276
00:22:46,233 --> 00:22:49,316
Big Bro, aren't we going
to look around Yunjing?

277
00:22:49,316 --> 00:22:50,829
Hello.

278
00:22:51,733 --> 00:22:53,167
Hello.

279
00:22:54,358 --> 00:22:55,970
I'm here to pick up a phone.

280
00:22:57,066 --> 00:22:58,358
A phone?

281
00:22:58,358 --> 00:23:00,733
Big Bro, you have a phone?

282
00:23:00,733 --> 00:23:02,566
It's an old one from Lv Qing.

283
00:23:02,566 --> 00:23:04,316
I brought it in for repairs.

284
00:23:04,316 --> 00:23:05,566
The manager has your phone.

285
00:23:05,566 --> 00:23:07,482
I'll go get him for you.

286
00:23:10,816 --> 00:23:12,275
This...

287
00:23:12,275 --> 00:23:13,566
It's all due to my lack of experience.

288
00:23:13,566 --> 00:23:15,134
Sorry to keep you waiting.

289
00:23:26,066 --> 00:23:27,233
It looks just like new.

290
00:23:27,233 --> 00:23:28,733
With the case replaced,
it looks exactly like a new one.

291
00:23:28,733 --> 00:23:30,442
See if you're satisfied with it.

292
00:23:31,900 --> 00:23:33,566
I am. How much is it?

293
00:23:33,566 --> 00:23:34,567
Don't worry about the money.

294
00:23:34,567 --> 00:23:37,025
I can't take your money.

295
00:23:37,025 --> 00:23:38,358
This device is still under warranty.

296
00:23:38,358 --> 00:23:40,441
No charge.

297
00:23:40,441 --> 00:23:41,860
Then, thank you.

298
00:23:42,733 --> 00:23:44,013
Let's go.

299
00:23:50,400 --> 00:23:52,316
I was wondering which girl

300
00:23:52,316 --> 00:23:54,441
he was spending so much money and effort on.

301
00:23:54,441 --> 00:23:56,358
He ordered two imported phones,

302
00:23:56,358 --> 00:23:58,400
stepped on one to give to him,

303
00:23:58,400 --> 00:24:01,858
and then swapped it for a brand new one.

304
00:24:01,858 --> 00:24:03,191
I didn't expect it to be a young man.

305
00:24:03,191 --> 00:24:04,233
Just focus on your own job.

306
00:24:04,233 --> 00:24:05,972
Stop gossiping.

307
00:24:09,233 --> 00:24:10,275
Big Bro.

308
00:24:10,275 --> 00:24:11,733
Didn't you say you were busy?

309
00:24:11,733 --> 00:24:13,441
I had to come even if I was busy.

310
00:24:13,441 --> 00:24:16,483
I wouldn't feel right leaving it to you.

311
00:24:16,483 --> 00:24:18,233
Besides, it's our parents'
first time in Yunjing.

312
00:24:18,233 --> 00:24:20,816
Fan Fan is much more capable now.

313
00:24:20,816 --> 00:24:22,066
He's a married man, after all.

314
00:24:22,066 --> 00:24:24,191
He's much more mature.

315
00:24:24,191 --> 00:24:26,650
Mom, like I was telling you,

316
00:24:26,650 --> 00:24:28,816
all the most developed countries

317
00:24:28,816 --> 00:24:30,233
are focusing on finance now.

318
00:24:30,233 --> 00:24:33,066
Making money with money is the fastest way.

319
00:24:33,066 --> 00:24:34,650
That doesn't sound very stable.

320
00:24:34,650 --> 00:24:36,150
It is stable!

321
00:24:36,150 --> 00:24:38,650
We have a client at our office.

322
00:24:38,650 --> 00:24:42,025
He just has a relative working
as a receptionist at a securities firm.

323
00:24:42,025 --> 00:24:43,358
He got a tip.

324
00:24:43,358 --> 00:24:45,066
In just one week,

325
00:24:45,066 --> 00:24:46,608
do you know how much he made?

326
00:24:46,608 --> 00:24:48,039
How much?

327
00:24:50,191 --> 00:24:51,816
- 30,000 yuan.
- How much?

328
00:24:51,816 --> 00:24:53,233
30,000 yuan?

329
00:24:53,233 --> 00:24:56,066
Fan Fan, is what your brother saying true?

330
00:24:56,066 --> 00:24:59,430
Mom, Dad, don't listen to his nonsense.

331
00:25:00,733 --> 00:25:05,650
How could a receptionist's information
be on the same level as Mr. Bei's?

332
00:25:05,650 --> 00:25:08,066
That's so much money.

333
00:25:08,066 --> 00:25:10,233
Trust your son.

334
00:25:10,233 --> 00:25:14,505
I have the brains, just not the opportunity.

335
00:25:17,608 --> 00:25:21,775
The eldest's brain is indeed
sharper than the second's.

336
00:25:21,775 --> 00:25:23,150
He's the big brother.

337
00:25:23,150 --> 00:25:24,900
It's no surprise he's doing better.

338
00:25:24,900 --> 00:25:26,566
Besides, if it weren't for Xiao Fan,

339
00:25:26,566 --> 00:25:27,983
could he have made it this far?

340
00:25:27,983 --> 00:25:30,025
Mom, don't keep bringing that up.

341
00:25:30,025 --> 00:25:31,650
Fan Fan stays at the Bei house every day,

342
00:25:31,650 --> 00:25:34,528
so why is he still just
a lowly salesperson after all this time?

343
00:25:35,983 --> 00:25:37,066
Lv Xin.

344
00:25:37,066 --> 00:25:39,066
Long time no see.

345
00:25:40,083 --> 00:25:42,166
Lv Xin is so pretty.

346
00:25:42,166 --> 00:25:43,500
Old Lu, do you remember?

347
00:25:43,500 --> 00:25:45,125
Back then, when the neighbors
looked at Lv Xin,

348
00:25:45,125 --> 00:25:47,375
they were so jealous.

349
00:25:47,375 --> 00:25:48,958
Just thinking about it makes me happy.

350
00:25:48,958 --> 00:25:51,541
No matter how jealous they were,
she's our daughter-in-law.

351
00:25:51,541 --> 00:25:55,125
I always thought Xiao Fan and Lv Xin
were the perfect match.

352
00:25:55,125 --> 00:25:56,916
And you didn't believe me.

353
00:25:58,150 --> 00:26:00,275
The stock market is complex,

354
00:26:00,275 --> 00:26:01,816
but there are plenty of opportunities.

355
00:26:01,816 --> 00:26:04,650
The key is to follow the right people.

356
00:26:04,650 --> 00:26:08,441
Even a pig can fly
if it's in the right place at the right time.

357
00:26:08,441 --> 00:26:11,191
When there's a pot of gold at home,

358
00:26:11,191 --> 00:26:13,549
why would we let outsiders get to it first?

359
00:26:16,691 --> 00:26:18,358
Lv Xin.

360
00:26:18,358 --> 00:26:19,400
Come here.

361
00:26:19,400 --> 00:26:21,523
I have something to ask you.

362
00:26:22,691 --> 00:26:24,130
What is it?

363
00:26:25,608 --> 00:26:28,293
Are stocks really that profitable?

364
00:26:29,233 --> 00:26:30,358
Yes.

365
00:26:30,358 --> 00:26:32,455
If you know how to invest,
you can make a lot of money.

366
00:26:33,400 --> 00:26:35,733
This boy of ours must be too dim-witted.

367
00:26:35,733 --> 00:26:38,191
That's why your father-in-law
won't help you make any money.

368
00:26:38,191 --> 00:26:39,566
Dad.

369
00:26:39,566 --> 00:26:42,025
You know what Fan Fan is like.

370
00:26:42,025 --> 00:26:43,650
It's no wonder that Mr. Bei

371
00:26:43,650 --> 00:26:47,025
doesn't help his own son-in-law get rich.

372
00:26:50,441 --> 00:26:52,608
My dad doesn't even trade stocks himself.

373
00:26:52,608 --> 00:26:54,430
Why would he involve Xiao Fan?

374
00:26:55,566 --> 00:26:57,066
Fan Fan, look at her.

375
00:26:57,066 --> 00:26:58,900
See how defensive she gets when I mention you?

376
00:26:58,900 --> 00:27:00,733
Enough. Mind your own business.

377
00:27:00,733 --> 00:27:02,940
Stay out of Fan Fan's affairs.

378
00:27:28,900 --> 00:27:31,400
Big Bro, it's getting late.

379
00:27:31,400 --> 00:27:33,858
You should head back now.

380
00:27:33,858 --> 00:27:35,108
I'm not going back.

381
00:27:35,108 --> 00:27:38,566
I took two days off
to spend time with Mom and Dad.

382
00:27:38,566 --> 00:27:40,816
But there's no room for you to stay here.

383
00:27:40,816 --> 00:27:43,998
Why don't you go find a hotel?

384
00:27:45,066 --> 00:27:46,858
Isn't Lv Qing away?

385
00:27:46,858 --> 00:27:48,608
I'll just stay in his room for now.

386
00:27:48,608 --> 00:27:50,963
I've already booked a hotel for you.

387
00:27:54,858 --> 00:27:58,816
Ping Ping, maybe you should
go stay at a guesthouse.

388
00:27:58,816 --> 00:28:02,650
Mom, why don't I just
sleep in the courtyard then?

389
00:28:02,650 --> 00:28:04,608
How was I to know that
staying at my brother's house

390
00:28:04,608 --> 00:28:06,566
meant there wouldn't even be a room for me?

391
00:28:06,566 --> 00:28:08,066
I didn't bring a letter
of introduction or my ID.

392
00:28:08,066 --> 00:28:09,441
How am I supposed to check in?

393
00:28:09,441 --> 00:28:12,066
No one is allowed to stay in my brother's room.

394
00:28:12,066 --> 00:28:13,191
Lv Xin.

395
00:28:13,191 --> 00:28:15,983
Do you just not want us staying at your house?

396
00:28:15,983 --> 00:28:19,233
Dad, Lv Xin didn't mean it like that.

397
00:28:19,233 --> 00:28:22,233
There are important documents
in Lv Qing's room.

398
00:28:22,233 --> 00:28:24,058
Big Bro Lv Qing is back.

399
00:28:29,566 --> 00:28:32,000
Mr. and Mrs. Lu, you're here.

400
00:28:34,941 --> 00:28:35,983
Lv Qing.

401
00:28:35,983 --> 00:28:38,025
Why have you lost so much weight
since the last time I saw you?

402
00:28:38,025 --> 00:28:39,816
No matter how busy you are,
you must look after your health.

403
00:28:39,816 --> 00:28:42,691
Big Bro Lv Qing, thank you for the bracelet.

404
00:28:42,691 --> 00:28:45,483
Thank you for your concern, Mrs. Lu.

405
00:28:45,483 --> 00:28:47,900
I brought some late-night snacks for everyone.

406
00:28:47,900 --> 00:28:50,483
Big Bro Lv Qing is so good to our family.

407
00:28:50,483 --> 00:28:54,691
My brother has been a lot of trouble
for you all these years.

408
00:28:54,691 --> 00:28:57,041
Xiao Fan hasn't been much trouble at all.

409
00:29:02,275 --> 00:29:03,566
What a huge mushroom!

410
00:29:03,566 --> 00:29:04,816
What are you talking about?

411
00:29:04,816 --> 00:29:05,816
This is abalone.

412
00:29:05,816 --> 00:29:07,733
It really does look like a mushroom.

413
00:29:07,733 --> 00:29:09,452
It does look a bit like one.

414
00:29:11,400 --> 00:29:12,733
Dad, Mom.

415
00:29:12,733 --> 00:29:14,483
This abalone is very expensive.

416
00:29:14,483 --> 00:29:15,691
Just one of these abalones...

417
00:29:15,691 --> 00:29:17,816
is worth as much as a pig back in our village.

418
00:29:17,816 --> 00:29:19,416
Right, Lv Qing?

419
00:29:20,900 --> 00:29:22,806
It's not quite that expensive.

420
00:29:24,441 --> 00:29:25,528
Here.

421
00:29:26,485 --> 00:29:27,971
Thank you, Mom.

422
00:29:38,191 --> 00:29:39,983
Big Bro.

423
00:29:39,983 --> 00:29:42,358
Big Bro Xiao Ping didn't bring his ID.

424
00:29:42,358 --> 00:29:43,928
He can't check into a guesthouse.

425
00:29:44,941 --> 00:29:46,358
The reason I came back...

426
00:29:46,358 --> 00:29:48,483
was to bring you all a little perk.

427
00:29:48,483 --> 00:29:50,233
A friend was dining out today

428
00:29:50,233 --> 00:29:53,400
and the hotel gave him two free stay vouchers.

429
00:29:53,400 --> 00:29:56,479
Since we're locals, we have no use for them.

430
00:30:00,691 --> 00:30:02,441
They're for two deluxe
standard rooms at a five-star hotel.

431
00:30:02,441 --> 00:30:04,713
I thought I shouldn't let them go to waste.

432
00:30:05,691 --> 00:30:07,858
So, I brought them back.

433
00:30:07,858 --> 00:30:10,233
I thought maybe one of you would like to go.

434
00:30:10,233 --> 00:30:11,868
I want to go!

435
00:30:14,858 --> 00:30:16,066
After we finish eating,

436
00:30:16,066 --> 00:30:18,733
I'll have Old Wu drive you there.

437
00:30:18,733 --> 00:30:20,650
Mr. and Mrs. Lu can share a room.

438
00:30:20,650 --> 00:30:22,825
As for Lu Xiao Ping...

439
00:30:25,608 --> 00:30:26,998
It's a pity.

440
00:30:27,983 --> 00:30:29,941
Since you don't have your ID,

441
00:30:29,941 --> 00:30:32,048
you can stay in Xiao Fan's room.

442
00:30:34,375 --> 00:30:36,083
Lv Qing is so thoughtful.

443
00:30:36,083 --> 00:30:37,917
Everything is arranged so well.

444
00:30:39,208 --> 00:30:40,000
Lv Qing,

445
00:30:40,000 --> 00:30:42,375
this must have cost you a lot, right?

446
00:30:42,375 --> 00:30:44,166
I feel a bit bad about this.

447
00:30:44,166 --> 00:30:45,166
Mrs. Lu,

448
00:30:45,166 --> 00:30:46,708
please, just enjoy your stay.

449
00:30:47,917 --> 00:30:49,625
Thank you, Lv Qing.

450
00:31:01,066 --> 00:31:02,066
Big Bro.

451
00:31:02,066 --> 00:31:04,588
You forgot your scarf last time.

452
00:31:12,775 --> 00:31:15,408
I actually bought this scarf for you.

453
00:31:17,150 --> 00:31:20,316
This... This scarf is way too expensive.

454
00:31:20,316 --> 00:31:21,650
I have no use for it.

455
00:31:21,650 --> 00:31:23,992
You... You should use it.

456
00:31:26,316 --> 00:31:28,509
If you don't want it, just throw it away.

457
00:32:21,533 --> 00:32:24,441
I got the phone fixed for you.

458
00:32:24,441 --> 00:32:26,501
I've already put the SIM card in.

459
00:32:27,900 --> 00:32:30,101
It's the kind that doesn't need top-ups.

460
00:32:31,483 --> 00:32:33,275
Big Bro.

461
00:32:33,275 --> 00:32:35,400
That phone looks brand new.

462
00:32:35,400 --> 00:32:38,981
Maybe... you should take it back and use it.

463
00:32:47,608 --> 00:32:49,109
It's fine.

464
00:32:50,733 --> 00:32:52,907
I bought another one for myself.

465
00:32:54,233 --> 00:32:56,407
You keep this one.

466
00:32:57,233 --> 00:33:01,965
From now on, make sure I can always find you.

467
00:33:03,441 --> 00:33:05,046
Do you hear me?

468
00:33:17,025 --> 00:33:19,447
Are you a dog or something?

469
00:33:26,733 --> 00:33:28,146
Big Bro...

470
00:33:40,775 --> 00:33:42,494
Fan Fan.

471
00:33:43,983 --> 00:33:46,991
Can we go back to how we were before?

472
00:34:07,900 --> 00:34:09,473
Before when?

473
00:34:27,275 --> 00:34:29,491
Once your parents leave,

474
00:34:30,275 --> 00:34:32,521
will you move back in with me?

